93
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:23,660
Pengasas hebat kita, Ymir, tak akan
mengharapkannya, jadi ia mustahil.

94
00:06:24,620 --> 00:06:25,790
Betul.

95
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:27,790
Akhirnya kamu faham, Zeke!

96
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:29,830
Ya!

97
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,159
Kalau awak tak ada semangat itu, keluar!

