pelan Euthanasia kita.]

282
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:43,160
[Awak mesti dapat cari orang itu.]

283
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:50,080
[Saya akan sentiasa menjaga awak.]

284
00:17:50,910 --> 00:17:51,910
