339
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:07,790
Apa awak cakap?

340
00:21:07,830 --> 00:21:09,080
Euthanasia?

341
00:21:09,870 --> 00:21:13,250
Awak akan mati di dalam mulut busuk Titan,

342
00:21:13,290 --> 00:21:16,910
